## Database
Supabase project: exbjodmnpdiayfzrdyux
NEVER create or modify migrations without explicit instruction
NEVER run DELETE or DROP commands
Role check uses user_restaurant_roles table — not user_profiles.role
No row in user_restaurant_roles = customer. Any row = staff.
Valid staff roles: owner | manager | server | host | kitchen | bar | staff
Table status default is "empty" — never "available"
reserved_at is a single timestamptz — never split date + time

## Rules — never break these
TypeScript strict — never use any
Never write Supabase queries in components — hooks only in /src/hooks/
Never call Claude API from client — Edge Functions only
Never use Claude for financial calculations
All money via formatCurrency(amount, "cad") — never template strings
All display text through i18n t() keys — never hardcode strings in JSX
All forms use react-hook-form + zod
No hardcoded hex colour values — Tailwind tokens only
No hardcoded tier names or subscription prices

